{
  "stem": "24137.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "He was always pulling, pulling my, my-- the clothes that I had, which were no clothes.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "You know, they took our clothes.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "It was just like a, a one dress and some kind of a pair of shoes without socks.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And he was always pulling me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And I-- my aunt would sleep the first one.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "Next to her was her daughter.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "Then it was my second aunt.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "Next to her was her baby.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "Then was my cousin, the one that was without a mother.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And then I was.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And this man was next to me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "So I always remember, I would climb over my cousin, climb over the baby, and climb next to my aunt.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And every time my aunt woke up, she says, what are you doing here?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Go back to your place, you know?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I said, I can't go back to my place.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because this man is annoying us-- annoying me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And she said, he's not annoying you.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Just, you know, sleep-- try to sleep.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Hindsight, I can't imagine how these two aunts who were themselves young, maybe in their 20s, had their own children, had now two other children, and had to take care of all of us-- didn't know what will be here, and had to cope with all of this.",
      "word_count": 48
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So they didn't have very much patience.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And one, one day, I remember they came and they opened the door.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they said, today is a special day.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We put some fire outside in a stove.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And you can all warm up your bread on the stove.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And you can all wash the, the underwear that you have in the water outside.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "There's a faucet.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And maybe you can keep it drying by this stove.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we-- everybody went out except the children.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
